		but was still listed as sci - fi,
		perhaps because it dealt with some kind of time travel.But,
		as in all good sci - fi,
		there was an underlying discussion about something much more compelling that made the story interesting.In one respect,
		finding out what that compelling and interesting subject mater is is what Phi - Fi.com is all about.

