			wasn’ t it a good thing that I had to stop at the market ? ”“Yes it was.”We got in line to pay
			for our purchases. < /blockquote>","post_title": "Arrival (2016) Review","post_excerpt": "","post_status": "inherit","comment_status": "closed","ping_status": "closed","post_password": "","post_name": "213-revision-v1","to_ping": "","pinged": "","post_modified": "2016-12-04 16:37:06","post_modified_gmt": "2016-12-05 00:37:06","post_content_filtered": "","post_parent": 213,"guid": "http:/ / phi - fi.com / 213 - revision - v1 / ","
